Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.07,0:04:22.70,JPN,,0,0,0,,{\3c&1A1A1A\4c&1A1A1A}義仲
Dialogue: 1,0:04:34.55,0:04:36.34,CN,,0,0,0,,{\3c&1A1A1A\4c&1A1A1A}賴朝戰敗了?
